    "en": {
      "title": "Four to the hospital from a clash in the Galumudoora struggle ground",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior spokesperson said that four people who suffered cuts and injuries were admitted to the Colombo National Hospital in a clash between two groups at the Galle mouth of struggle ground.",
        "The spokesman said that three youths aged 15, 17 and 20 years old residing in Colombo 15 and an 18-year-old youth residing in Wellampitiya area are among them.",
        "The spokesperson added that all the injured are being treated in Ward No. 72"
      ],
